msgid "ping storm"
msgstr "ping storm"

#: ../../P/ping-storm.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../P/ping-storm.rst:9
msgid ""
"A form of :ref:`DoS-attack` consisting of a flood of :ref:`ping` requests "
"(normally used to check network conditions) designed to disrupt the normal "
"activity of a system. This act is sometimes called ping lashing or ping "
"flood. Compare :ref:`mail-storm`\\, :ref:`broadcast-storm`\\."
msgstr ""
"システムの正常な活動を妨害するために設計された、(通常はネットワーク状態を確認するために使われる)\\ :ref:`ping`\\ "
"リクエストの洪水から成る\\ :ref:`DoS-attack`\\ の一形態。この行為はping lashingやping "
"floodと呼ばれることもある。\\ :ref:`mail-storm`\\ 、\\ :ref:`broadcast-storm`\\ と比較せよ。"
